"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Welcome, welcome.\r\nWhat do you want to do today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Okay, then. Please drop in again\r\nif you're ever in the mood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "This store is known for our Lullaby Battle Royale,\r\na blazing battle against our top three players."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "If you want to compete, you'll have to meet the\r\nfollowing conditions and pay a participation fee."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry, but it looks like you don't\r\nqualify for the battle royale right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Come back and talk to me once\r\nyou manage to meet the conditions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Congrats! You're qualified for our battle royale!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "All you have to do now is pay the participation\r\nfee and you'll be ready to rumble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "If you finish between 2nd place and 4th place,\r\nyour participation fee will go down the drain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "But if you somehow beat our champions,\r\nyou'll net a pretty hefty profit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "So, what'll it be? Do you want to\r\ntake on the Lullaby Battle Royale?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but you don't have enough cash\r\nto cover your participation fee."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Talk to me again once you have\r\na little more money on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Great, just hand over that fee and we'll be\r\nready to roll. Good luck... You'll need it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Got it. Just talk to me again if you ever\r\nfeel like giving the battle royale a shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Nice try there. Please drop in again\r\nif you're ever in the mood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Congrats on your 1st place finish! Please\r\ndrop in again if you're ever in the mood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "If you wanna do the battle royale again,\r\nyou'll have to meet the conditions again, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Here's the point bonuses our parlor offers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Welcome, sir. What are you\r\nlooking to do today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Very well, then. We greatly\r\nanticipate your next visit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "This store plays host to the Modern Battle Royale,\r\nwhich pits you against our top mahjong experts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "If you wish to compete, we ask that you fulfill\r\nthese requirements and pay us a participation fee."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately, it appears as though you\r\ndo not meet the necessary conditions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Please return to this desk and notify me once\r\nyou have fulfilled the tasks at hand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Congratulations, sir. You currently meet\r\nthe requirements for battle royale participation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "In order to continue onward to the event,\r\nyou must now pay your participation fee."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Please note that you will lose that fee if\r\nyou do not finish at the head of the table."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "However, if you do indeed manage to win,\r\nyou will receive quite a generous prize sum."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Now then, what will you do, sir? Do you wish\r\nto compete in the Modern Battle Royale?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "It appears as though you lack the money\r\nnecessary to cover your participation fee."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Please return to this desk and notify me once\r\nyou have the required funds in your possession."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Excellent. Allow me to take your participation\r\nfee, then. I wish you the best of luck today, sir."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Very well, sir. Please return to this desk and\r\nnotify me if you ever gain the necessary courage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "That was a good attempt, sir. We look forward\r\nto your continued patronage in the future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Well met, sir. Winning the table is quite the feat!\r\nWe look forward to your continued patronage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "If you wish to compete in the battle royale again,\r\nwe ask that you once again fulfill our requirements."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "At this establishment, you will receive the\r\nfollowing bonus points depending on your rank."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Yo, how 'bout a bit of mahjong? As you can\r\nprobably tell, we're not the greatest players."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "If you wanna play, it'll cost ya 12,500 yen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Mkay, then. Fork up that cool 12,500."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "That's a damn shame... I guess just\r\ncome back when you wanna play with us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Hey, you wanna play mahjong with us?\r\nIf you do, it'll run ya 12,500 yen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "That was a real hoot.\r\nCome back sometime, ya hear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "You up for some mahjong?\r\nWe're kinda good, if I do say so myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "If you're looking to jump in, you'll\r\nhave to pay the 25,000 yen entry fee."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "All righty. Just hand over that\r\n25,000 and we'll be ready to go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Well that's a downer... Just come talk\r\nto me if you ever wanna play, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "You down to throw down, mahjong style?\r\nIt'll cost you 25,000 to play at this table."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "They say luck changes with the tides...\r\nWell, let's give it another go sometime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Are you interested in some mahjong?\r\nWe are all pretty decent players."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "If you'd like to join us, we only\r\nask that you put up 25,000 yen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Wonderful. I'll be taking that 25,000 then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Oh, I see... Well then, please come speak\r\nto us again if you're ever interested."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Do you want to play with us? You'll just\r\nneed to put in 25,000 yen to join."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "That was a good match.\r\nLet's play together again sometime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Could I interest you in a round of mahjong?\r\nThough I must warn you, we are quite advanced."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "If you wish to participate, we require\r\nthat you place a 50,000 yen bet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Splendid. Now the 50,000, please."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "How unfortunate. If you ever wish to put your\r\nmahjong mettle to the test, please return to us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Has our table piqued your interest? You will\r\nneed to place a 50,000 yen bet to join us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "My word... That result was quite unexpected.\r\nLet us play again in the near future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Oh, uh... Never mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Let's see what this battle royale is all about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "No, maybe some other time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll give it a shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "No, I think I'll pass."
msgstr ""

